=== 本·罗伯茨-史密斯 ===
2011年1月23日，澳洲特种空勤团的[[本·罗伯茨-史密斯|本·罗伯茨-史密斯]]（{{lang|en|Ben Roberts-Smith}}）[[下士|下士]]成为第二位澳大利亚维多利亚十字勋章得主<ref name="SAS digger awarded VC">{{cite news | last = AAP | title = SAS digger awarded VC for taking on Taliban | accessdate = 2014-09-08 | newspaper = The Sydney Morning Herald | date = 2010-01-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140107080958/http://www.smh.com.au/national/sas-digger-awarded-vc-for-taking-on-taliban-20110123-1a0zd.html | archivedate = 2014-01-07 | deadurl = no | publisher = Fairfax Media | url = http://www.smh.com.au/national/sas-digger-awarded-vc-for-taking-on-taliban-20110123-1a0zd.html}}</ref>。罗伯茨-史密斯下士于2010年6月11日在阿富汗的战事中单枪匹马对抗并摧毁了两处[[塔利班|塔利班]][[机枪|机枪]]据点<ref name="SAS digger awarded VC" />，新闻报道中将这一英勇行径与[[爱德华·肯纳|爱德华·肯纳]]（{{lang|en|Edward Kenna}}）获维多利亚十字勋章的行动相提并论<ref name="Second SAS Afghan Victoria Cross">{{cite news | last = Dodd | first = Mark | title = Second SAS Afghan Victoria Cross for heroic charge | accessdate = 2014-09-08 | newspaper = The Australian | date = 2010-01-21 | publisher = News Limited | archivedate = 2013-03-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130326083713/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/national-affairs/second-sas-afghan-victoria-cross-for-heroic-charge/story-fn59niix-1225991997101 | url = http://www.theaustralian.com.au/national-affairs/second-sas-afghan-victoria-cross-for-heroic-charge/story-fn59niix-1225991997101?nk=1d9713a6675e67964c5622025aff92e5}}</ref>。罗伯茨-史密斯下士还曾于2006年获得[[英勇勋章|英勇勋章]]，获得维多利亚十字勋章后，他成为澳大利亚国防军中战功最卓著的现役军人<ref name="SAS digger awarded VC" />。

=== 丹尼尔·凯阮 ===
2012年11月1日，[[澳大利亚皇家团第6营|澳大利亚皇家-{zh-tw:團; zh-hans:团; zh-hk:軍團}-第6营]]的[[丹尼尔·凯阮|丹尼尔·凯阮]]（{{lang|en|Daniel Keighran}}）下士因2010年8月在阿富汗战争中的表现获澳大利亚维多利亚十字勋章。凯阮下士故意把自己暴露在敌军炮火之下，将火力引离一位受伤的战友及其他正在照顾伤员的人。凯阮是此等勋章的第三位得主，也是首位不属特种部队的受勛者。<ref name="Keighran">{{cite news | title = RAR soldier awarded Victoria Cross for Afghan valour | url = http://www.abc.net.au/news/2012-11-01/rar-soldier-awarded-victoria-cross-for-afghan-valour/4345848 | accessdate = 2014-09-08 | newspaper = ABC News | date = 2012-11-01 | archive-date = 2016-10-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161031002836/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2012-11-01/rar-soldier-awarded-victoria-cross-for-afghan-valour/4345848 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Soldier Honoured with Victoria Cross | url = http://www.army.gov.au/Our-work/News-and-media/Australian-Soldier-Honoured-with-Victoria-Cross | accessdate = 2013-05-24 | newspaper = Army News | date = 2012-11-01 | archivedate = 2013-05-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130524221627/http://www.army.gov.au/Our-work/News-and-media/Australian-Soldier-Honoured-with-Victoria-Cross}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Corporal Daniel Alan Keighran, VC | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130520201029/http://army.gov.au/Our-work/News-and-media/Australian-Soldier-Honoured-with-Victoria-Cross/Corporal-Daniel-Alan-Keighran | accessdate = 2013-05-20 | newspaper = Army News | url = http://www.army.gov.au/Our-work/News-and-media/Australian-Soldier-Honoured-with-Victoria-Cross/Corporal-Daniel-Alan-Keighran | date = 2012-11-01 | archivedate = 2013-05-20}}</ref>

=== 卡麥隆·贝尔德 ===
2014年2月13日，[[澳大利亚总理|澳大利亚总理]][[托尼·阿博特|托尼·阿博特]]宣布特种部队第2突击团的[[卡麥隆·贝尔德|卡麥隆·贝尔德]]（{{lang|en|Cameron Baird}}）下士获追授维多利亚十字勋章。贝尔德下士曾于2007年获英勇勋章，之后于2013年在阿富汗阵亡。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-02-13/abbott-announces-100th-victoria-cross-recipient/5257200 | title = Victoria Cross: Corporal Cameron Baird becomes 100th recipient, PM Tony Abbott tells Parliament | publisher = ABC News | date = 2014-02-13 | accessdate = 2014-09-08 | archivedate = 2014-06-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140615123519/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-02-13/abbott-announces-100th-victoria-cross-recipient/5257200}}</ref>

== 追授勋章提议 ==
2001年4月3日，[[澳大利亚参议院|澳大利亚参议员]]克里斯·沙赫特（{{lang|en|Chris Schacht}}）表示，他会在上任次日提出《2001年澳大利亚维多利亚十字勋章奖励草案》（{{lang|en|''Award of Victoria Cross for Australia Bill 2001''}}），建议追授数枚澳大利亚维多利亚十字勋章。2001年4月4日，参议员沙赫特提出草案，提议追授3位前澳大利亚军人这一勋章。<ref name="Hansard0401">{{cite web | url = http://www.aph.gov.au/Hansard/senate/dailys/ds040401.pdf | format = PDF | title = Parliamentary Debates, Senate | publisher = Hansard | date = 2001-04-01 | accessdate = 2011-12-20 | pages = 87-89 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111220065607/http://www.aph.gov.au/hansard/senate/dailys/ds040401.pdf | archivedate = 2011-12-20 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>草案经过首读后，沙赫特发表二读致辞，表示通过草案授予澳大利亚维多利亚十字勋章虽有超越国会立法权的可能，但他认为，《[[澳洲联邦宪法|澳洲联邦宪法]]》第51条第6项中授予了议会“联邦和各州的海军和陆军防卫”权力，所以国会应该对荣誉和奖项方法同样有权提出立法，按照正常程序进行辩论后休会。2001年6月1日，来自[[布莱登_(澳大利亚国会选区)|布莱登]]的众议员[[希德·赛德巴顿|希德·赛德巴顿]]（{{lang|en|Sid Sidebottom}}）提出了《2001年国防法令修訂（维多利亚十字勋章）草案》（{{lang|en|''Defence Act Amendment (Victoria Cross) Bill 2001''}}）。该草案与参议员沙赫特提出的类似，赛德巴顿同样认为国会根据《澳洲联邦宪法》第51条第6项拥有立法权。<ref name="Hansard0601" />这两项草案在[[2001年澳大利亚联邦选举|2001年澳大利亚联邦选举]]前都没有再经过辩论。沙赫特和赛德巴顿均为[[澳大利亚工党|澳大利亚工党]]成员，该党当时属反对党，并且这个问题也由反对党领袖[[金·比兹利|金·比兹利]]列入接下来的联邦选举竞选活动中<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090922182007/http://www.ozpolitics.info/election2004/2001ALP/veterans.pdf | archivedate = 2009-09-22 | url = http://www.ozpolitics.info/election2004/2001ALP/veterans.pdf | format = PDF | title = Kim Beazley's plans for veterans | publisher = Australian Labor Party | year = 2001 | accessdate = 2009-09-22 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，提议通过这样的奖励“提高三位澳大利亚普通人的知名度和认可度，他们都表现出了杰出的英勇行为”<ref name="Hansard0601">{{cite web | url = http://www.aph.gov.au/HANSARD/reps/dailys/dr040601.pdf | title = Parliamentary Debates, House of Representatives | date = 2001-06-01 | publisher = Hansard | format = PDF | accessdate = 2011-11-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111124083712/http://aph.gov.au/hansard/reps/dailys/dr040601.pdf | pages = 20–23 | archivedate = 2011-11-24 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

提议追授勋章的三人分别是[[约翰·辛普森·柯克帕特里克|约翰·辛普森·柯克帕特里克]]（{{lang|en|John Simpson Kirkpatrick}}）、阿尔伯特·克利（{{lang|en|Albert Cleary}}）和[[泰迪·希恩|泰迪·希恩]]（{{lang|en|Teddy Sheean}}），他们均是因在第一或第二次世界大战中的英勇行为获得追授提议。其中辛普森的故事已成为澳大利亚传奇<ref name="Anzacs">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140724021014/http://www.anzacs.net/Simpson.htm | url = http://www.anzacs.net/Simpson.htm | title = Australia's favourite hero | publisher = Anzacs | accessdate = 2014-09-08 | archivedate = 2014-07-24}}</ref>，他曾是[[澳大利亚皇家陆军医疗队|澳大利亚陆军医疗队]]第三澳大利亚战地救护队成员，于一战期间在盖利博卢半岛参加加里波利之战。1915年4月25日降落在[[澳新军团湾|澳新军团湾]]后，他从第一晚就开始用一头驴从火线上把伤员拉到海滩撤离。他如此坚持了三个半星期，其中许多情况下都冒着敌人的炮火，直到壮烈牺牲。但是，[[乔治五世_(英国)|英王乔治五世]]于1919年下旨，不会再针对刚刚结束的一战授予奖励。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Wilson | first = Graham | title = The Donkey Vote. A VC for Simpson — The Case Against | journal = Sabretache: the Journal and Proceedings of the Military Historical Society of Australia | volume = 47 | issue = 4 | date = 2006-12 | pages = 25–37}}</ref>

1965年，一场号召授予辛普森维多利亚十字勋章的宣传活动使得他与一头驴的形象出现在澳新军团纪念章的正面，这一纪念章于1966年宣布制作，1967年首度发布。工党在[[2007年澳大利亚联邦大选|2007年澳大利亚联邦大选]]中获胜，所以有人猜测2001年的草案会重新提出。历史学家安东尼·斯汤顿（{{lang|en|Anthony Staunton}}）在《澳大利亚军事史期刊》（{{lang|en|''Australian Journal of Military History''}}）撰文指出，澳大利亚维多利亚十字勋章不应予以追授。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.shieldsgazette.com/news/local-news/bravery-award-for-war-hero-blocked-1-1285897 | title = Bravery award for war hero blocked | date = 2008-01-15 | work = The Shields Gazette | last = Myles-Kelly | first = Paul | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120902090950/http://www.shieldsgazette.com/news/local-news/bravery-award-for-war-hero-blocked-1-1285897 | archivedate = 2012-09-02 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2012-09-02}}</ref>2011年4月13日，有报道称澳大利亚联邦政府的国防授勋及嘉奖事务上诉审裁处将对13例追授奖励的英勇行为进行审议。审裁处首先就会对“13人获得维多利亚十字勋章、澳大利亚维多利亚十字勋章或其它形式认可的资格”进行讨论，然后再继续对各人的实际情况加以探讨<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121107225214/http://www.smh.com.au/national/awards-tribunal-to-consider-13-posthumous-vcs-20110416-1dihi.html | title = Awards tribunal to consider 13 posthumous VCs | newspaper = The Sydney Morning Herald | publisher = Fairfax Media | date = 2011-04-16 | archivedate = 2012-11-07 | url = http://www.smh.com.au/national/awards-tribunal-to-consider-13-posthumous-vcs-20110416-1dihi.html}}</ref>。最终该部门于2013年2月6日向政府提交了报告，建议不予追授任何奖励<ref>{{cite web | title = Inquiry into unresolved recognition for past acts of naval and military gallantry and valour | accessdate = 2014-09-09 | work = Defence Honours and Awards Appeals Tribunal | publisher = Australian government | archivedate = 2014-06-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140607000337/http://defence-honours-tribunal.gov.au/inquiries/completed-inquiries/valour/ | url = http://defence-honours-tribunal.gov.au/inquiries/completed-inquiries/valour/ }}</ref>。

